      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "起点是Clinical Engineer在Azure Backup Vault上配置备份策略，配置完之后Azure才会去触发实际的备份作业。所以第一步是ClinEng指向Azure的\"Configure policy\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
