        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Azure向Workload VM触发快照和备份作业，这是虚线返回，表示异步触发。然后Workload VM完成备份后，要把恢复点信息回传给Azure。这两步都是Azure和Workload之间的双向交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
